66
00:05:10,111 --> 00:05:12,111
Cukup luar biasa, bukan?

67
00:05:14,811 --> 00:05:16,911
Oh, airnya mulai mengering.

68
00:05:16,911 --> 00:05:18,211
Yah, benar.

69
00:05:21,511 --> 00:05:24,611
Luar biasa betapa baiknya ini berfungsi.

70
00:05:29,311 --> 00:05:32,411
"Misteri Taman Batu Mengalir Air Jepang"

71
00:05:32,411 --> 00:05:33,711
"(Bagian 1)"

72
00:05:38,611 --> 00:05:41,511
Jika kau suka, bisakah kita pergi ke salon

73
