86
00:06:47,011 --> 00:06:48,511
Silahkan ke sebelah sini.

87
00:06:48,511 --> 00:06:50,411
Oh, terima kasih, terima kasih.

88
00:06:51,511 --> 00:06:52,811
Itu pria yang baru kita lihat beberapa waktu lalu.

89
00:06:52,811 --> 00:06:54,011
Yah.

90
00:06:54,011 --> 00:06:56,311
