146
00:09:33,811 --> 00:09:35,911
Jadi, aku selalu membawanya.

147
00:09:38,011 --> 00:09:39,411
Baik, ini dia.

148
00:09:39,411 --> 00:09:41,511
Terima kasih banyak!

149
00:09:41,511 --> 00:09:43,811
Silahkan datang dengan teman-temanmu.

150
00:09:43,811 --> 00:09:46,411
Ya, pasti!

151
00:09:46,411 --> 00:09:49,511
Namun, aku tidak tahu kau terkait

152
00:09:49,511 --> 00:09:51,811
