178
00:11:04,411 --> 00:11:05,711
Bintang-bintang...

179
00:11:05,711 --> 00:11:07,411
Terima kasih sudah menunggu.

180
00:11:08,311 --> 00:11:10,011
Ini datang birnya!

181
00:11:11,611 --> 00:11:13,911
