182
00:11:13,911 --> 00:11:16,411
Jika kau mau, kami punya minuman selain bir juga.

183
00:11:16,411 --> 00:11:18,311
Aku akan bawakan kau cangkir lainnya.

184
00:11:18,311 --> 00:11:21,211
