186
00:11:23,011 --> 00:11:25,211
Hei! Hentikan, Ayah.

187
00:11:25,211 --> 00:11:28,011
Hei, hei! Hentikan! Jangan tumpahkan itu!

188
00:11:28,011 --> 00:11:30,611
Sayang sekali!

189
00:11:30,611 --> 00:11:34,611
Oh astaga, bicara tentang kecanduan minuman keras.

190
00:11:52,311 --> 00:11:53,911
